Titolo: Hyper Lode Runner

Anno: 1989

Descrizione: Hyper Lode Runner is a video game for the Game Boy from Bandai released in 1989 in Japan and  1990 in North America. It is based on the 1983 game Lode Runner from Broderbund. While each level in the original fit on a single screen, Hyper Lode Runner has a scrolling playfield.